  "title": "QA/QC",
  "description": "<h4><strong>Job Description:</strong></h4>\n<p>• Ensure quality of works in accordance with Quality Management Plan including development of Method Statements, Inspection &amp; Testing Plans and Checklists. Should know process of handling, storage and handover process of such materials.</p>\n<p>• Monitor the implementation of the Project Quality and Environmental Plan.</p>\n<p>• Assist QAQC Manager in preparing Quality Plan that supports the project and clients’ requirements on quality assurance (QA) and quality control (QC).</p>\n<p>• Prepare and conduct site inspections and close on the reports.</p>\n<p>• Witnessing and sentencing of all site inspections within their disciplines.</p>\n<p>• Follow and fill up the inspection and test plans to comply with the contract requirements.</p>\n<p>• Ability to conduct inspection and test plans and Inspecting works and recording all inspections to ensure compliance as required.</p>\n<p>• Acquaint section personnel with QA requirements and arrangements in place to achieve them.</p>\n<p>• Audit and monitor QA and Environmental systems for compliance and effectiveness.</p>\n<p>• Coordinating and maintaining a non-conformance control system including issuing of non-conformance reports to the Project Manager and ensure corrective actions are implemented and effective.</p>\n<p>• Control/check on status of issue/revisions of QC documents/drawings within section/on sites.</p>\n<p>• Ensure all QA/QC control measures and procedures are documented, implemented and auditable.</p>\n<p>• Assist QAQC Manager in managing document control.</p>\n<p>• Maintaining the quality assurance records and execution of periodic inspection on job.</p>\n<p>• Verify that all quality related activities are in accordance with codes and standards.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proven experience in the construction industry.</li>\n  <li>In-depth knowledge of construction quality control/assurance principles and practices.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in construction management software and QA/QC documentation tools.</li>\n</ul>",
